#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("This is the end of the line. The data from the Malphas scan has identified the 'Singularity Anchor'—the device that keeps the Void node stable. If we destroy it, the node will collapse.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("The SD Malphas has moved to the core to protect the Anchor. We are taking the Erebus in. She’s falling apart, but she’ll give us the sensor lock we need.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("Once the Anchor is gone, the node will begin to collapse. You will have a thirty-second window to jump out before the rift seals forever. Lead us one last time.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


